          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-22-1696338833659-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-22-1696338833659-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice your <strong>cucumber</strong> finely into discs</p><p>Add the <strong>cucumber discs</strong> and the<strong> remaining cider vinegar</strong> to a bowl with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Stir everything together and set aside – this is your<strong> quick-pickled cucumber</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
